# Profile Site Conventions

1. Route map is fixed to `/`, `/about`, `/work`, `/projects`, `/contact`.
2. Layout source of truth is `.cursor/plans/design-spec.md` (derived from paper wireframes).
3. Use amber-forward styling via shared classes such as `.text-amber` and `.btn-amber`.
4. Use fixed typography scale only; avoid fluid font sizing techniques.
5. Store profile content in `lib/data/profile.ts`; avoid hardcoding long content directly in page JSX.
6. Keep project visuals under `public/projects/` and render through `next/image`.
7. Feedback submission must go through `POST /api/feedback`.
8. No UI implementation until `design-spec.md` is user-approved.
9. If wireframe design changes, update `design-spec.md` before changing UI implementation.
